FT  02 MAR 93 / UK Company News: Sharp decline to Pounds 80,651 at Goodwin
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Goodwin, the Stoke-on-Trent engineering company, reported pre-tax profits
for the six months to October 31 of Pounds 80,651, a little more than a
third of the comparable Pounds 232,040.
